# Optional: only needed if you want a server-side fallback key for local dev
# or for self-hosted demos. The app is BYOK (bring your own key) by default —
# the key is collected from the user in-browser on first run and stored in
# their browser's localStorage, never on the server.
#
# Two key types are supported (either one works):
#
#  - Google AI Studio key ("AIza...") — FREE tier, no credit card.
#    Get one at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#    Image generation runs on gemini-2.5-flash-image (Nano Banana).
#
#  - OpenRouter key ("sk-or-...") — paid, unlocks more models
#    (Gemini 3 Pro/Flash Image, GPT-5.4 Image 2).
#    Get one at: https://openrouter.ai/keys

GOOGLE_API_KEY=
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
